description: Welcome to 601-611 East Broadway, Unit 201, in the heart of South Boston with deeded parking and two outdoor spaces! This stunning 2-bed, 2-bath condo offers a spacious living space, perfect for those seeking comfort and convenience. Step inside to discover an open-concept layout featuring elegant hardwood floors that flow seamlessly throughout the living area. The unit is equipped with central AC and forced air heating, ensuring year-round comfort. The kitchen boasts ample cabinetry and is designed to accommodate your culinary adventures. Adjacent to the kitchen, the living and dining areas provide a welcoming space for relaxation and entertainment. Retreat to the primary bedroom, which includes a full bath and plenty of closet space. The second bedroom is equally inviting and versatile, ideal for guests or a home office. Enjoy the convenience of in-unit laundry. This condo is situated in a prime location with all that Southie has to offer right outside of your front door.
